Item 5.07. Submission of Matters to a Vote of Security Holders.
 
The annual meeting of stockholders of ATMI, Inc. (the Company) was held on May 22, 2013.  As of March 27, 2013, the record date for the meeting, 33,029,427 shares of ATMI common stock were outstanding.  A quorum consisting of 29,906,474 shares of common stock were present or represented at the meeting. The stockholders elected each of the Companys nominees for Class I director, approved the compensation of the Companys named executive officers on an advisory basis, and ratified the appointment of Ernst & Young LLP as the Companys independent registered public accounting firm for the fiscal year ending December 31, 2013.  The following tables represent the votes tabulated for each of these matters.
 
